/// steers more forecast mass toward the line that paid — Hotelling repositioning
/// toward realized demand. As the routing converges, the predicted hit rate
/// (hence %c) climbs monotonically toward the attention/Hotelling equilibrium.
///
/// Lean: `Gnosis.MycelialMeshAttentionHotelling.vent_shift_pulls_hit_rate_up`;
/// gnosis-math `Gnosis.SignalFusion.added_source_above_baseline_pulls_fusion_up_cross`.
